  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary aim of the project is to examine the efficacy of the Psychiatric Rehabilitation
      Weight Loss program in reduction of weight and body mass index (BMI.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study involves 144 individuals who will be randomly assigned to the intervention group or
      treatment as usual group(control group). All Participants will undergo baseline assessment,
      assessment at week 12, week 24 and in year from baseline.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
